<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>IPv4<sp/>address<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>machine<sp/>in<sp/>dotted<sp/>notation,<sp/>or<sp/>the<sp/>literal<sp/>value<sp/>&apos;dhcp&apos;</highlight></codeline>
